                "rank": 1,
                "score": 178.3,
                "message": "核四的問題，沒有那麼困難。看你考慮的是未來四年、未來十年還是未來一百年。",
                "from_id": "136845026417486",
                "from_picture": "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash2/t1.0-1/c149.53.662.662/s200x200/295050_209249939176994_1185044525_n.jpg",
